This is an wishlist of features to add in future releases, in no
particular order:

* Documentation (man/info/HTML ??)
* Complete test suite
* Fix all FIXMEs
* Debug and/or Verbose mode
* l10n ??
* PATCHES in SRC_URI
* Additional cygclasses:
	- bzr
	- cross
	- docbook
	- doxygen
	- relocate: http://cygwin.com/ml/cygwin/2006-10/msg00743.html
	- xfce
* Additional mirrors:
	- debian
	- gentoo
	- kernel
	- mysql
* dolocale
* dosed
* automatically remove empty dirs in D; keepdir()
* wget --no-check-certificate
* mixed download protocols: http://cygwin.com/ml/cygwin/2006-11/msg00137.html
* Windows shortcuts for X11 programs
	doico /path/to/pixmap.png [calls png(to|2)ico and doins]
	make_win_shortcut Foo [run.exe foo.exe -wait --display=...]
